    ├── constants.ts
    └── client/
```

## Naming Conventions

| Type              | Pattern                         | Example                          |
| ----------------- | ------------------------------- | -------------------------------- |
| Server action     | `[method]-*-action.ts`          | `get-todos-action.ts`            |
| Client query hook | `use-[method]-*-query.ts`       | `use-get-todos-query.ts`         |
| Mutation hook     | `[method]-[entity]-mutation.ts` | `post-todo-mutation.ts`          |
| Pure requests     | `requests.ts`                   | `entities/todo/api/requests.ts`  |
| Query constants   | `constants.ts`                  | `entities/todo/api/constants.ts` |
